      "comment": "UNCLE STILTSKIN (5) has a strong winning strike-rate this journey having won three of six starts. Missed the frame latest (30.28) when seventh over 515m at this track in a Grade 5. Has the ability and should feature. PAW GRADY (2) is mixing form lately, finishing out of the placings last time at The Meadows but was a Grade 5 winner two back at this track. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. BILLY RAY MIKADO (1) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 2.25 lengths at Bendigo in a handy 24.29 beating Goosebumps Rico. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. PAW QWERTY (3) bold run expected on best form.",
